d of fuel, should greatly\noutnumber active ones; observational constraints would not then be stringent\nuntil we had observed enough candidates to constitute a proper ensemble\naverage.(abridged)\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2008 08:43:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Apr 2009 20:08:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
