tension of the Standard Model (the nuMSM), both mass and\nthe mixing angle of the DM sterile neutrino are bounded from above and below,\nwhich suggests the possibility for its experimental search.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2008 14:51:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2009 22:54:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-03-31"}
