{10},\n189 -- 371 (1989), Eq. (8.4-4)] -- sum the divergent series occurring in this\ncontext effectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Aug 2008 14:57:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
